  Header Mega Menu - Supplements (snippet wrapper)

  Renders the static theme block `header-mega-menu-supplements` so it can be
  included from the desktop header navigation.

  Note: The `supplements_menu` parameter is accepted for API compatibility with
  `header-desktop-nav`, but the underlying block derives its own data from the
  supplements collection, metafields, or block settings.

  @param {linklist} supplements_menu - Optional secondary menu (currently unused)

  @example
  {% render 'header-mega-menu-supplements', supplements_menu: supplements_menu %}
{% enddoc %}

